    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143990/extras/f5484c4673e66c182ab8ca8835b26164.avif?t=1734010665\" width=616 height=169 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2>Poland under martial law. There has been an accident in a secret soviet base near Krzyżowiec. Monsters came out and started terrorizing the town. If you don't stop them to spread out, this will increase the tension between the west and east. You will meet the residents of Krzyżowiec<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143990/extras/3c5025612045f325ad43d07dd703fa74.avif?t=1734010665\" width=616 height=250 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Reload mechanic</h2>Due to the limited budget of Polish army, you are issued with one magazine. You will need to load the round manually so better be prepered before the fight!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143990/extras/f726d4d1dbfb7a701340e9ab9e69ae34.avif?t=1734010665\" width=616 height=200 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Cold war horror investigation story<br></li><li> Manual reloading mechanic<br></li><li> Enemies with diffrent behaviours<br></li><li> Unique setting<br></li><li> Retro stylized graphics</li></ul>",
